name: Mira Tuu
description:
I love life and want to share it with a special person and create a family with him. What I can say about myself. I am a person of strong moral values and principles. A creative, sensitive and sincere. I am faithful, reliable, kind care, tender. In my free time I like to spend it with my close relatives and friends. I like to take care about my pets. I believe in real love and I think that it is the most beautiful thing in the world!.
I am looking for a man who can treat his woman with love and respect. I want to meet a mature man who is older than me and understands and knows what he wants. I want to love and be loved.
